WEBVTT

1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
Step one, set up the distillation apparatus.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,000
The typical distillation apparatus consists of a burner,

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:14,000
a distillation flask containing the substance we want to distill,

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:18,000
a thermometer, a condenser, a receiving flask,

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:23,000
and some corks to connect the components.
